  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Retail Business Manager",
  "description": "<p><strong>Location:</strong> Orchard<br /><strong>Work Schedule:</strong> 5-day work week (inclusive of weekends & PH)<br />Shifts: 9:30am–6:30pm / 12:30pm–9:30pm<br /><strong>Compensation:</strong> Competitive Salary + Allowances + Variable Bonus + AWS</p><h3><strong>Role Overview</strong></h3><p>As a Retail Manager, you will be the custodian of the brand, driving commercial performance while delivering an exceptional, personalised client experience. You will lead, inspire, and develop a high-performing team, ensuring the boutique consistently reflects the prestige and standards of a luxury environment.</p><h3><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></h3><ul><li><p>Oversee all retail operations to achieve sales, profitability, and service excellence goals.</p></li><li><p>Lead from the sales floor, coaching teams to deliver refined, personalised, and memorable client experiences.</p></li><li><p>Build, manage, and grow a strong portfolio of VIP and loyal clients through relationship management and CRM excellence.</p></li><li><p>Recruit, train, and develop boutique teams to uphold luxury service, grooming, and selling standards.</p></li><li><p>Ensure impeccable boutique presentation, visual merchandising, and product display in line with brand guidelines.</p></li><li><p>Analyze sales performance, manage inventory, and ensure stock integrity and loss prevention.</p></li><li><p>Partner with internal teams on marketing initiatives, digital engagement, and online business growth.</p></li><li><p>Ensure full compliance with brand, operational, and security standards.</p></li></ul>",
